name: Pink Lip PAINT
description:
A fresh new lip gloss that contains collagen peptides to increase lip volume and reduce lip wrinkles, while doubling as an amazing moisturizer. These collagen peptides rapidly speed up cell renewal to increase lip size safely and painlessly. A whisper lightweight treatment, that is luxuriously moisture-rich comfortable to wear, and never sticky. The gloss creates a super natural, luscious look.

Net Weight .14 fl oz / 4.37ml

Made In USA

Key points to remember:

Doubles as a treatment
Will not feather or bleed
Reduces lip wrinkles
Feels smooth and light on the lips 
Comfortable to wear and never sticky
Contains collagen peptides which increases lip volume
